		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2"><a name="102607917574087"></a><span class="msgSubject">Whoops</span><br clear="all" />
		   <span class="sm">Posted: Jul  7th  2002 at  6:10pm EDT<span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a class="sm" href="/db/item.html?item=2179&amp;start=0;mid=102607917574087#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a> </span></span></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" class="mform" ><span class="fs8"><span class="notbold">By: </span><a href="/db/poster.html?user=174031"><span class="">BattleLordKhan</span></a><b><span class=""></span></b>
		   <br /><span class="nobr"><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Excellent  </span><br />
<br/><a href="/db/item.html?item=2179;page=1;howmany=50#102607917574087"><img alt="" title="Use this to create a link to this post" src="/shared/garrowrt.png" border="0" height="9" width="11" /> Link to this post</a>
<br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1" alt=""/></span></td>
<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>got a bit hasty with the enter button there.  Anyways, for my assessment- This is one of the best cold resist pieces of armor for an affordable price and an out of the way slot.  What I mean by this is the fact that there aren't many low-mid end cloaks worth their prices with great stats.  Whatever cloak you were wearing before is probably dispensable for this one, especially if you are doing velious dragon raids or play on pvp with the constant threat of wizard ice nukes.  You'd be surprised at how this 20 svc piece of armor can cripple an ice comet's damage. All in all- fellow pvpers, go out and buy this cloak, it is cheap so you can afford to lose it! I'd say buy for 100 or less, don't be impatient and pay more (as long as its reasonable go with it). Also I'm not sure what faction it hurts if any in Everfrost, but this mob is around 30ish, in case you want to check it out for yourself.</p>
<br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />Caribizzou Khan <br />45th Tunare Ranger <br />Rallos Zek <br />Elven Crusaders</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="fs8"></td><td align="right" class="fs8" >1 reply</td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
