		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2"><a name="100750402930334"></a><span class="msgSubject">The Elusive Marter Icebear and his fuzzy cloak</span><br clear="all" />
		   <span class="sm">Posted: Dec  4th  2001 at  6:13pm EDT<span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a class="sm" href="/db/item.html?item=2179&amp;start=0;mid=100750402930334#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a> </span></span></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" class="mform" ><span class="fs8"><span class="notbold">By: </span><a href="/db/poster.html?user=125017"><span class="Sage">SamanthieSnowheart</span></a><b><span class="Sage"><br/>Sage</span></b><br /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" />
		   <br /><span class="nobr"><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Good  </span><br />
<br/><a href="/db/item.html?item=2179;page=1;howmany=50#100750402930334"><img alt="" title="Use this to create a link to this post" src="/shared/garrowrt.png" border="0" height="9" width="11" /> Link to this post</a>
<br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1" alt=""/></span></td>
<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>Aloha all and well met. <br /> <br />I seek to add to the wealth of information on this evil man, so that he may be hunted and slain. <br /> <br />The Evil Marter Icebear tends to spawn on the flats around the Perma Frost gates.  In hunting this man, a party of 26's can accomplish the task, but be wary - he hits very hard.  A pair of hunters might include a druid/ranger/bard (for tracking) and complementary class for the battle, and the pair should be around 28th season for the hunt.  A solo artist can accomplish the mission at around 31, but that is class and equipment dependant. <br /> <br />I have slain this foul man many times, and have found his cloak to be a very quick sale for 100pp each.  Sadly, I have not the time to wait for the best possible price. <br /> <br />If you have the time, follow this evil man along his path.  Starting from his birthsite near Perma he takes a meandering path that leads him arcoss the front of the Mammie Ruins (much to the bane of many a fallen Mamie hunter ...), then a lazy path to Megan's Tower and then heading over to the Bandl Flats region. <br /> <br />Sometimes, by the grace of the gods, another beast will spawn in his place.  I have seen such forms as a &quot;ice goblin whelp&quot; and &quot; a polar bear cub&quot; spawn in his absence.  It is most unusual to see a cub so far out on the tundra near the Mammie Ruins - slay it and head for the Perma Frost gate and keep tracking. <br /> <br />I wish the well future hunters of Marter Icebear for this fine cloak. <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /></p>
<br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />Huntress Samanthie Snowheart <br />Half-elf Karana Warder of Surefall Glade <br />65 seasons and more -- sniffing the trails of Norrath <br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=369799" title="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=369799" target="akztarg">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_pr...?num=369799</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="fs8"></td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
