		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2"><a name="98036091911632"></a><span class="msgSubject">Not Rare, Martar and Karg drop</span><br clear="all" />
		   <span class="sm">Posted: Jan 24th  2001 at  7:31pm EDT<span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a class="sm" href="/db/item.html?item=2179&amp;start=0;mid=98036091911632#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a> </span></span></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" class="mform2" ><span class="fs8"><span class="notbold">By: </span><a href="/db/poster.html?user=23208"><span class="">Kenshen</span></a><b><span class=""></span></b>
		   <br /><span class="nobr"><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Excellent  </span><br />
<br/><a href="/db/item.html?item=2179;page=1;howmany=50#98036091911632"><img alt="" title="Use this to create a link to this post" src="/shared/garrowrt.png" border="0" height="9" width="11" /> Link to this post</a>
<br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1" alt=""/></span></td>
<td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%">
<p>This is dropped almost all the time by Karg and I've only seen Martar killed once and he had it on him too. <br />-Rangers (lvl 13-18) you can get this Cloak in exchange for helping a higher level character Kill Karg.  You can Track Karg down while your hunting Mammoth calfs and Orc Mountaineers.  Often higher level characters will pay rangers to give them a &quot;tell&quot; when you find him so that they can kill him for his RARE sword drop. (highly saught after item).  Just ask for the cloak in exchange for your services. <br />-Druids (lvl 20+) this strategy works since you now get track but at around this you should have a better &quot;back&quot; item anyways (unless your fighting Cold magic creatures).  <br /> <br />Again, a good AC item as well as a high Cold resist.  Good item to have.</p>
<br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />------------------ <br />Kilick - LvL 26 Druid <br />Istanbol - LvL 25 Warrior <br />Cazic-thule</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="fs8"></td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
